      "body" : "My initial understanding was that a floating relay fee implies a floating dust threshold.\r\n\r\nTo satisfy that outputs are not uneconomic, this seems reasonable, however, this comes at the cost of needing more information to determine the threshold. Whether this is an issue or not for meta protocols, this seems to affect non-full-nodes in general.",
