      "body" : "By checking the code, currently fee of a transaction depends on the dust present. (Dust are added to the fee)\r\nHowever, if we need fee for determining dust then we get circular dependency, maybe not so easy to implement as I thought. :(\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n// Never create dust outputs; if we would, just\r\n// add the dust to the fee.\r\nif (newTxOut.IsDust(::minRelayTxFee))\r\n{\r\n    nFeeRet += nChange;\r\n    reservekey.ReturnKey();\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
      "created_at" : "2015-10-15T03:35:24Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/6824#issuecomment-148272519",
      "id" : 148272519,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/6824",
      "updated_at" : "2015-10-15T03:37:20Z",
      "url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/comments/148272519",
      "user" : {
         "avatar_url" : "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3020646?v=3",
         "events_url" : "https://api.github.com/users/NicolasDorier/events{/privacy}",
         "followers_url" : "https://api.github.com/users/NicolasDorier/followers",
